\f0\b\fs54 \cf0 Coffee Glaze\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl320\ql\qnatural

\fs48 \cf0 Ingredients\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\ql\qnatural

\f1\b0\fs46 \cf0 1/4 cup whipping cream\
1 tablespoon coffee liqueur (recommended: Kahlua)\
2 teaspoons espresso powder\
2 cups powdered sugar\
Water, as needed\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl320\ql\qnatural

\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 Directions\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\ql\qnatural

\f1\b0\fs46 \cf0 In a medium bowl, whisk together the cream, coffee liqueur, and espresso powder until smooth. With a wooden spoon, gradually stir in the powdered sugar until smooth. If the glaze is too thick, stir in the water, 1/4 teaspoon at a time.\
\
